      "content": "I hear you, and it’s clear you’ve been through a lot. But sometimes, the world can be too harsh, and it’s easy to feel like you’ve been stripped of everything. If you’re feeling this way, it might be worth considering that there’s a different path out there, one where you can find a new sense of purpose. It might not be easy, but it’s never too late to start over and redefine who you are.",
      "source": "target",
