      "content": "I understand that it feels like the weight of the world is on your shoulders, and it’s okay to feel overwhelmed. But giving up might not be the answer. There are people who care about you and your kids, and they want to see you happy and thriving. Maybe it’s time to reach out for help, to talk to someone who can guide you through this tough time. You don’t have to face this alone. There’s always a chance for recovery, even from the deepest of falls.",
